  "summary": {
    "en": "Custom DIY FORTS color-box set for brand orders, with adjustable artwork, piece mix, colors, and packing details.",
    "zh": "DIY FORTS 彩盒定制款，可调整盒面、件数、配色和包装内容。"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": [
      "DIY FORTS 3+ is a made-to-order color-box set for private-label or exclusive retail packs.",
      "The set uses PP plastic rods and connector balls. Children insert and twist the rods to build forts, tents, rockets, houses, tunnels, and other play structures.",
      "Logo, box artwork, manual, piece count, rod colors, connector colors, and carton marks can be adjusted.",
      "No public price is shown. Quotation follows confirmed artwork, configuration, quantity, and packing."
    ],
    "zh": [
      "DIY FORTS 3+ 为彩盒定制款，可做贴牌包装或渠道专版。",
      "产品采用 PP 塑料杆件和连接球，插入后旋转固定，可搭建城堡、帐篷、火箭、房屋、隧道等造型。",
      "LOGO、彩盒画面、说明书、件数、杆件颜色、连接球颜色和外箱唛头都可以调整。",
      "不公开标价，确认画面、配置、数量和包装后报价。"
    ]
  },
